{"tid":980259,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫卡：裁員德國 加大對華攻勢","createTime":"2019-01-13T11:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T09:10:34.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94c729a70c507c0383f253949a85f99af397fee7","tid":980259,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"庫卡：裁員德國 加大對華攻勢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190112-%E5%BA%AB%E5%8D%A1%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E6%94%BB%E5%8B%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190112-%25E5%25BA%25AB%25E5%258D%25A1%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2594%25BB%25E5%258B%25A2&d=O0Ck5FDcW8taR8KUalswujACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=4ccd3fd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190112-%E5%BA%AB%E5%8D%A1%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E6%94%BB%E5%8B%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n據德國《商報》和《奧格斯堡彙報》報道，被中國電器大王美的收購的德國機器人生產商庫卡（Kuka）計畫通過節約政策和加大在中國市場的攻勢來扭轉危機。庫卡臨時總裁Peter Mohnen 於周五推出了應急方案，這其中包括到2021年節省成本3億歐元。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，與業主美的的合作也將得到改善。一個德中專業小組將促進雙方的合作。<br />\n<br />\n原來一直興旺的庫卡銷售開始下跌。2017年還有35億歐元的營業額，2018年只有32億歐元，幾乎下跌了10%。庫卡現下調了企業中期目標。Mohnen 表示，庫卡銷售不佳，與汽車工業處境困難和中國經濟增長放緩有關。<br />\n<br />\n據員工透露，是美的催促庫卡節約成本。而前財務總監Mohnen推出應急方案，也是要爭取成為正式總裁。<span style=\"color: red;\">節約計畫包括削減IT、管理、營銷等多項開支。這意味着公司在德國也將裁員。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由於美的收購庫卡後，曾擔保庫卡在德國的基地和工作崗位到2023年不會受到損害，庫卡現將裁員，引發驚訝。但Mohnen表示：&ldquo;我們不得不這樣做。&rdquo;<br />\n</span></span><br />\n庫卡恰恰是在最被看好的中國市場上發展不利。中國人覺得庫卡機器人有的太貴，而庫卡有時又不能及時供貨。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">庫卡計畫在中國擴大生產，為亞洲市場研製簡單、較小的比如可用於電氣工業的機器人  。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n庫卡在德國備受關注。2016年，美的砸下40多億歐元，併購了庫卡，在德國引發了對中資戰略併購的顧慮。隨後，德國收緊對外經濟法，加大了中資收購德企的難度。"},{"pid":"9e1e41687cd4f59a9eecdfd553ea98cc92d4669b","tid":980259,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"又係IT9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a9e210890f5273390aaf0323e2c4965c9ec459","tid":980259,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7ed0429f278aad63377ce6643d7fcd7d338ec2","tid":980259,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T13:23:13.000Z","msg":"德國工人唔出嚟抗議？<br />\n買完就話炒人"},{"pid":"128f5a5fcc992f933c834ce410752751eda41a32","tid":980259,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"支那收購完通常都蝕錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945fe279ce54ad810c2f1b8ff9d712594c38da3e","tid":980259,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"話你唔夠平，搞到你做唔到生意，逼你將成間野係中國設廠，偷盡晒d技術再賤傾收購你。然後政府補貼番間野，反傾銷robotic arm番歐洲市場，夾撚死你其他廠<br />\n<br />\n當初以係賣左都制衡到支那，你德國佬以為自己係聖人？"},{"pid":"f926b68fc7bc31538f8d66bf41aa528b55176100","tid":980259,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea961a921a4ca71bf2b84913889be5769cf1f356","tid":980259,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"德國佬幾時先醒呢"},{"pid":"6dbd63478db82d00719a0221fa